  "detailed_description": "Hoversteppers is a freestyle hoverboard skating game. Explore stages, complete challenges against the clock, or freestyle your own way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558930/extras/0f7190354612490468d14729a3bd14e9.poster.avif?t=1728688799\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558930/extras/0f7190354612490468d14729a3bd14e9.webm?t=1728688799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558930/extras/0f7190354612490468d14729a3bd14e9.mp4?t=1728688799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 unique stages<br></li><li>Over 50 challenges to complete<br></li><li>Unlockable characters, boards, and cosmetics<br></li><li>A rich soundtrack of jungle / drum and bass, by talented artists Mr. Wax, Lunanescence, and Snowdream<br></li><li>Multiple achievements to unlock</li></ul>",
